          <a href="?tab=accademia#accademia" data-landing-tab="accademia" class="group rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl xl:p-4">
