          </a>

          <a href="?tab=eventi#eventi" data-landing-tab="eventi" class="group rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl xl:p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-700">Eventi e Community</p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-950">Vivi il percorso</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600 xl:leading-5">Incontri, camminate, attività e momenti di comunità sul territorio.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700 xl:mt-3">Guarda <span class="ml-1 transition group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span></span>
          </a>
          <a href="?tab=filosofia#filosofia" data-landing-tab="filosofia" class="group rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl xl:p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-700">Il libro</p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-950">Il corpo, un mondo da scoprire</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600 xl:leading-5">Dalla PosturaCorretta all'agriturismo rigenerativo Il Giardino del Corpo.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700 xl:mt-3">Scopri il libro <span class="ml-1 transition group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span></span>
          </a>

          <a href="?tab=collabora#collabora" data-landing-tab="collabora" class="group rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl xl:p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-700">Progetti</p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-950">In corso</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600 xl:leading-5">Aggiornamenti, cantieri aperti e prossimi sviluppi del progetto.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700 xl:mt-3">Leggi gli aggiornamenti <span class="ml-1 transition group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span></span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- PERCORSO -->
  <!-- PERCORSO -->
<div id="percorso" data-tab-panel="percorso" class="<%= "hidden" unless active_landing_tab == "percorso" %>">

  <section class="flex min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] items-center px-5 py-6 md:py-10">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.25fr_0.75fr] lg:items-stretch xl:gap-12">

