            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-blue-700">
              Percorso personalizzato
            </p>

            <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950 md:text-5xl md:leading-[1.05]">
              Costruisci <span class="text-blue-700">il tuo percorso</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
              Con le metodiche posturali abbiamo scelto di mettere al centro il corpo. Seleziona uno o più bisogni della tua situazione attuale per tracciare il tuo percorso di salute personalizzato.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- CHOICE FORM -->
          <div class="border-t border-slate-200 pt-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">
              In cosa vuoi essere aiutato?
            </h2>

            <!-- 7 CHOICE CARDS -->
            <div class="mt-4 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
              <button type="button" data-choice="Cura e Riabilitazione" data-path-key="cura"
                class="pc-choice rounded-2xl border border-red-200 bg-white p-4 text-left transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-red-700">Cura</p>
                <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-slate-950 leading-5">Cura e Riabilitazione</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500">Hai dolore, sintomi o una patologia?</p>
              </button>

              <button type="button" data-choice="Prevenzione" data-path-key="prevenzione"
                class="pc-choice rounded-2xl border border-orange-200 bg-white p-4 text-left transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-orange-700">Prevenzione</p>
                <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-slate-950 leading-5">Prevenzione</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500">Lavoro, sport o età?</p>
              </button>

              <button type="button" data-choice="Performance" data-path-key="performance"
                class="pc-choice rounded-2xl border border-yellow-200 bg-white p-4 text-left transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-yellow-700">Performance</p>
                <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-slate-950 leading-5">Performance</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500">Lavoro, studio o IA?</p>
              </button>

              <button type="button" data-choice="Benessere Integrato" data-path-key="benessere"
                class="pc-choice rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200 bg-white p-4 text-left transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-700">Benessere</p>
                <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-slate-950 leading-5">Benessere Integrato</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500">Salute, energia e qualità della vita?</p>
              </button>

              <button type="button" data-choice="Postura e Fisiologia" data-path-key="fisiologia"
                class="pc-choice rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-white p-4 text-left transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
